   Dergarabedian said he believes overall business can increase
again next year and noted that trailers now playing for several
year 2000 films, including ``Mission: Impossible 2,'' ``Dinosaur''
and ``Gone in 60 Seconds,'' have already generated significant
excitement among customers.
</P>
<P>
   XXX
</P>
</TEXT>
