   LAMB-COLUMN _ Social connection is as important for doctors to
measure as weight, cholesterol and blood pressure, says Dr. Brooks
S. Edwards, medical editor of the Mayo Clinic Health Oasis Web
site. ``The strength of our relationships has great bearing on how
well we age, how well we deal with life's challenges and how well
