   SECURITY-HOLIDAY _The holiday season is supposed to be a time of
good cheer, but it's also a time when home burglaries are at their
highest, according to law enforcement experts. Burglary is a crime
of opportunity where the objective is to get in and out of a home
as quickly as possible. But by following a few basic guidelines you
can discourage unwanted intruders from ever attempting to get in.
(AHill, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH ILLUSTRATION.
