something, you'll get it done.'' &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL; 
</P>
<ANNOTATION>
    &UR; (STORY CAN END HERE AT 625 OR CONTINUE TO 1,050) &LR;  &QC; 
</ANNOTATION>
 &LR;  &QL;
