</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN. Business Editors: Looking ahead to 2000...)   (This 650-word ``separate-buy'' financial story is from the
December issue of ``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it
must be purchased from the New York Times Syndicate's sales
representative DEBRA WEYDERT at 732-390-4480, or fax her at
732-390-4697. Her e-mail address is weyded(at)nytimes.com. If
unable to reach Ms. Weydert, please call 800-444-0267, or fax us at
816-822-1444.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been filed into the ``f'' financial
news, ``i'' international news and ``a'' domestic/general news
files.)  
  
