five-year effort, American troops are pulling out of Haiti. And so,
after America's sixth invasion this century, Haiti could find
itself dropping from the radar screens of the Clinton
administration just as it prepares to vote for a parliament. By
John Donnelly. (2 takes) PHOTOS
