another myth: To set a festive dinner table, matching china,
matching glassware and matching napkins are musts. Sometimes,
inexpensive colored glass says ``festive'' as much as anything.
From left, stemware in blue, $3.95, Crate &AMP; Barrel; pink, $6, and
gold, $7, Pier 1 Imports; and ruby red, $9.95, Crate &AMP; Barrel.
