   (NYT1) BOSTON -- Dec. 14, 1999 -- KRUGMAN-COLUMN-MUG -- The New
York Times' new Op-Ed columnist, Paul Krugman. Krugman is an
economics professor at the Massachusetts Institute of Technology
and an author known for his theories on international trade and
economics. (Diane Barros/The New York Times)
</P>
